Class CompareDiagrams

java.lang.Object
  edu.neu.csye.clubuml2012.compareAlgorithm.CompareDiagrams

public class CompareDiagrams
extends java.lang.Object

CompareDiagrams class implements an application that simply compares 2 UML diagrams It takes 2 String type parameters which are path of EcoreDiagram files find out differences between these diagrams writes these differences into a pdf file and returns the path of this pdf file
